   ## Task 3:
    
    Cloud functions > create function > name > http:cloud stora, event type: on (finalizing/creating) file in the selected bucket, bucket:select bucket > save > next > runtime: “the functions is written in” > entry point: <entry point>, inline editor: paste code from files (index and package) > deploy >> 5 MINUTES
    
